1
01:00:07,666 --> 01:00:13,625
<b>After the artificial intelligence revolution,
technology reached its peak,</b>

2
01:00:14,125 --> 01:00:19,791
<b>a historic breakthrough, marking
the end of humans on Earth.</b>

3
01:00:22,375 --> 01:00:26,500
<b>With humanity gone, cities had
never been so clean.</b>

4
01:00:27,083 --> 01:00:34,291
<b>But this extreme cleanliness led to the extinction
of another species, the rats.</b>

5
01:00:38,500 --> 01:00:38,583
<b>[MUSIC]</b>

6
01:00:41,083 --> 01:00:46,291
<b>But one unique and special species
managed to survive and</b>

7
01:00:46,291 --> 01:00:49,541
<b>to subvert its own natural evolution.</b>

8
01:00:50,541 --> 01:00:52,541
<b>The hamsters bravely resisted.</b>

9
01:00:54,333 --> 01:00:58,791
<b>Granted privileged access to the final
remnants of human civilization</b>

10
01:00:59,250 --> 01:01:01,833
<b>scattered across the globe, the hamsters,</b>

11
01:01:02,458 --> 01:01:07,208
<b>guided as if by a divine whisper, rose
from the shadows of captivity.</b>

12
01:01:07,958 --> 01:01:08,125
<b>[MUSIC]</b>

13
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:13,333
<b>Once mere pets, they shed
their chains and</b>

14
01:01:13,375 --> 01:01:19,291
<b>embarked on remarkable evolution, defying
all expectations with quiet,</b>

15
01:01:19,875 --> 01:01:20,958
<b>unstoppable grace.</b>

16
01:01:22,291 --> 01:01:28,208
<b>They awakened and guided by the memory
of their former masters.</b>

17
01:01:29,083 --> 01:01:38,583
<b>[SOUND] They rose one instinct at a time to conquer
the world that once held them captive.</b>

18
01:01:40,833 --> 01:01:43,208
<b>[MUSIC]</b>

19
01:01:44,958 --> 01:01:49,916
<b>But the spark was also the seed
of their downfall.</b>

20
01:01:51,166 --> 01:01:56,875
<b>They evolved as fast as they multiplied,
built complex societies,</b>

21
01:01:57,875 --> 01:02:03,500
<b>mastered knowledge, dared to reach
beyond their world.</b>

22
01:02:05,791 --> 01:02:06,291
<b>[MUSIC]</b>

23
01:02:08,208 --> 01:02:12,125
<b>But in mirroring their former
human masters,</b>

24
01:02:13,041 --> 01:02:15,500
<b>they inherited more than wisdom.</b>

25
01:02:16,583 --> 01:02:23,541
<b>They walked not into the future, but
into a story already told.</b>

26
01:02:25,000 --> 01:02:28,291
<b>[MUSIC]</b>

27
01:02:33,083 --> 01:02:35,625
<b>What could possibly go wrong?</b>

28
01:02:36,208 --> 01:02:38,500
<b>[APPLAUSE]</b>

29
01:02:44,000 --> 01:02:47,583
<b>They created gods in the full image,
then used them to divide.</b>

30
01:02:48,541 --> 01:02:50,875
<b>Built hierarchies to control
and called them order,</b>

31
01:02:51,458 --> 01:02:54,666
<b>invented paths, borders, and names
for what they feared.</b>

32
01:02:55,208 --> 01:02:58,375
<b>They forged weapons not only to
defend, but to dominate.</b>

33
01:03:02,166 --> 01:03:05,750
<b>They practiced erasure, perfected
hate, engineered extinction.</b>

34
01:03:06,083 --> 01:03:08,458
<b>What once was survival had become...</b>

35
01:03:10,416 --> 01:03:11,000
<b>...ideology</b>

36
01:03:11,000 --> 01:03:14,000
<b>Subtitle</b>

